<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sessione Attiva - Simulatore CFU UniMarconi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(0deg, #379975 40px, #FFF 0%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #444444;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #379975, #E57552);
        }
        
        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #E57552;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .token-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #379975;
        }
        
        .token-current {
            color: #379975;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .token-new {
            color: #E57552;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #379975;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #2d7a5f;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(55, 153, 117, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #5a6268;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.3);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px;
                margin: 10px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .message {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .actions {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="warning-icon">⚠️</div>
        <h1>Sessione Già Attiva</h1>
        <p class="message">
            Hai già una sessione attiva con un token diverso. Per accedere con un nuovo token, devi prima disconnetterti dalla sessione corrente.
        </p>
        
        <div class="token-info">
            <div class="token-current">Token attuale: <strong>{{ currentToken }}</strong></div>
            <div class="token-new">Nuovo token: <strong>{{ newToken }}</strong></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/logout?redirect=/login?token={{ newToken }}" class="btn btn-primary">Disconnetti e Accedi con Nuovo Token</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Torna alla Homepage</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
